Extractors¶

def get_orgs(bs):
    try:
        orgs = (bs
        .find('dl',{'class': 'ui-ncbi-toggler-slave'})
        .find_all('dd'))
        return [o.get_text() for o in orgs]
    except:
        return 'ORGANIZATION_NA'

def get_kwords(bs):
    try:
        return (bs
           .find('div', {'class': 'keywords'})
           .find('p')
           .get_text()
           .split())
    except:
        return 'KEYWORDS_NA'
